          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 23,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Venti_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "溫迪",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "溫迪的傷害大部分是由元素戰技/元素爆發組成的，而元素爆發期間，溫迪幾乎都不會上場。溫迪使用該武器，幾乎能常駐滿層特效加成，雖然啟動時間比較長，但也是比較適合副C溫迪的四星武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 38,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Fischl_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "菲謝爾",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "菲謝爾如果在隊伍中擔任副C角色，大部分傷害都是在後臺由奧茲造成的，所以該武器對菲謝爾來說也是四星武器中一個不錯的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kujou Sara_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "九條裟羅",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器的高基礎攻擊力可以提高九條裟羅",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "提升的效果，同時武器特效也可以有效提高九條裟羅元素爆發造成的傷害。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
